00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:55,360 --> 00:02:00,000
Go Ahead

3
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:02,950
Episode 8

4
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,560
The child knows nothing.

5
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:12,800
As adults,

6
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:14,200
we should arrange

7
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,200
the child's future

8
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,400
as early as possible.

9
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:18,280
Even if I take him home,

10
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,560
you can rest assured,

11
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:21,000
because I won't stop him

12
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,200
from contacting you.

13
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,660
After all, you brought him up.

14
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:25,840
Well. Stop.

15
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:28,280
In our family, we respect

16
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,640
the children's opinions.

17
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:30,440
What is he going to do in the future,

18
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:31,400
and what school he will go to...

19
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,730
You are narrow-minded.

20
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,000
Sorry.

21
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,360
I didn't mean to

22
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,680
look down upon you.

23
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:42,440
After all, you run a noodles restaurant,

24
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:44,320
so you have limited field of vision.

25
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:45,120
You know what?

26
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:46,240
Nowadays, those families,

27
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,880
as long as they have conditions,

28
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:48,720
give the best to their children

29
00:02:48,720 --> 00:02:50,120
with all their might.

30
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:51,680
Even if they have to surrender their last resource,

31
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,800
they want their children

32
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,200
to have a bright future, right?

33
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:55,400
Enough. Stop it.

34
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:57,160
I'll talk to Ziqiu.

35
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:58,120
That's it.

36
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,560
Why does what I said

37
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,720
make no sense to you?

38
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:06,560
If you keep the child here like this,

39
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:08,090
he won't have a good future.

40
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:09,400
Your purpose is

41
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:12,120
to let him take care of you when you are old, right?

42
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,040
Don't you want to take him back

43
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:14,560
and let him continue your family?

44
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,240
Come on.

45
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,440
He is my son

46
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:17,840
and I want to take him back.

47
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:19,720
Is there anything wrong with that?

48
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:21,980
The only difference between you and me is

49
00:03:22,079 --> 00:03:24,120
that I can give all my family property

50
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,400
to him in the future.

51
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,400
But you keep him here.

52
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,720
You are hindering his development, aren't you?

53
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:29,240
I'm doing this for his own good.

54
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:29,960
For his own good?

55
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:31,220
What did you do before?

56
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:32,880
Get out of here.

57
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:33,400
No.

58
00:03:34,079 --> 00:03:35,040
Wait. I got it.

59
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:39,460
You think one million yuan is too little, right?

60
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:42,680
Even if you put ten statues of the God of Wealth here,

61
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,920
in this small noodles restaurant,

62
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:44,800
how many years will it take you to earn

63
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:45,800
one million yuan?

64
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:46,380
Tell me.

65
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:48,200
How much on earth do you want?

66
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:49,930
Don't talk about money with me.

67
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,040
I earn money

68
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:52,360
by my own hands.

69
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:53,400
If I take money from you,

70
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,280
I feel sick.

71
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:55,000
Get out of here!

72
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:55,930
Get out! Get out!

73
00:03:56,079 --> 00:03:56,540
Get out!

74
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:57,780
Get out of here!

75
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:00,520
Li Haichao,

76
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,640
what do you mean?

77
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:03,400
I'm telling you. Doing this

78
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,040
is no good to

79
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,480
us at all.

80
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,160
You are unreasonable.

81
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,400
Who are you?

82
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,560
Why did Haichao

83
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,520
drive you out?

84
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,269
I,

85
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:19,240
I'm He Ziqiu's dad.

86
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,720
He Ziqiu's dad?

87
00:04:21,070 --> 00:04:21,480
Yes.

88
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:23,530
I'm his biological dad.

89
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,280
May I know your surname?

90
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:29,040
My surname is Zhao.

91
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:29,840
Bah!

92
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,360
You are shameless.

93
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:32,480
What bastard are you?

94
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,840
Why do you abuse me?

95
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:34,640
I abuse you?

96
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,480
Are you a man?

97
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:36,680
There are people everywhere in the street.

98
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,040
Why don't I abuse anyone else?

99
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,040
You are a bastard.

100
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,080
Haichao,

101
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:41,280
don't be polite to him.

102
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,040
Do you have boiled water here?

103
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,360
Splash water to drive him away.

104
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,720
You have no manners.

105
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,440
You are unreasonable.

106
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,760
Who is unreasonable?

107
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:50,159
You.

108
00:04:50,159 --> 00:04:51,320
Who is unreasonable?

109
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:52,200
Stop there!

110
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:53,120
You bastard!

111
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:56,460
What's wrong with you?

112
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,320
I'm exhausted.

113
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,480
I haven't finished the assignments

114
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,540
our teachers gave,

115
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:05,120
but the teachers at the cram school gave a lot of assignments.

116
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:06,680
If a machine is invented

117
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,960
to help people do homework,

118
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:09,290
that will be wonderful.

119
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,760
You wish.

120
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:17,400
Didn't Ling Xiao and Ziqiu come here with you?

121
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:18,720
They are going to take part in the National College Entrance Examination.

122
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:20,380
So, they are studying at home.

123
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,900
It's good that they are studying.

124
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:23,880
I thought

125
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:24,960
that because of Zhao Huaguang,

126
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:26,690
Ziqiu doesn't dare to come out.

127
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,600
That's impossible.

128
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:29,760
Ziqiu said

129
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,600
that Zhao Huaguang didn't come to him again.

130
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,240
Moreover,

131
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:33,000
last time when Zhao Huaguang

132
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,880
went to see my dad,

133
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:34,960
Mrs. Qian in our community

134
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:36,760
was going to splash water on him.

135
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:38,900
I guess he doesn't dare to come again.

136
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:45,620
What do you want me to go with you to do?

137
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,159
Mr. Huang called me,

138
00:06:47,159 --> 00:06:48,680
asking me to give the notes I took in class this week

139
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:49,680
to Tang Can.

140
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:51,600
She'll be absent from school again next week.

141
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:54,440
She hasn't finished making up last week's missed lessons yet.

142
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,120
No wonder

143
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:57,000
she had to transfer to another school and repeat a year.

144
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,159
She asks for leave so often.

145
00:06:58,159 --> 00:06:59,520
Even if she went to study in Grade 5 at primary school,

146
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:00,640
she wouldn't be able to keep pace with the others.

147
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:02,080
No need to give the notes to her.

148
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:03,120
They won't be useful for her.

149
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,920
She won't understand even if she sees them.

150
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:07,000
I don't know whether she can understand.

151
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,240
But this is a task Mr. Huang gave me,

152
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,570
so I have to complete it.

153
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:10,770
Let's go.

154
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:13,160
She has to catch a plane in the afternoon.

155
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,280
Can I say no?

156
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:17,440
Let's go. Let's go.

157
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:18,760
Come on.

158
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:19,450
Let's go.

159
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:37,250
There's something wrong with her.

160
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:38,800
On such a hot day,

161
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:40,600
we come to give her the notes,

162
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,040
but she keeps us outside,

163
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:44,159
without treating us to drinks.

164
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:47,250
That's something unexpected.

165
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:49,000
But it makes sense.

166
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,640
Something was wrong with this girl

167
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,920
long ago.

168
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,159
She's too much.

169
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:55,900
She's really too much.

170
00:07:57,960 --> 00:07:58,920
It's so hot.

171
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:00,560
Stop talking.

172
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:01,960
So depressed.

173
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:03,000
Stop talking.

174
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:07,560
Sorry for bothering you to come here.

175
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,800
I suddenly received an audition notice.

176
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:12,530
I'm going to Beijing and stay there for a few days.

177
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:15,320
We've been waiting for you for half an hour.

178
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:17,160
I was packing up.

179
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:20,000
You were packing up,

180
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,120
so you kept the two of us

181
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,680
waiting in the sun?

182
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,240
I'm sorry.

183
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,240
I don't like

184
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:28,200
to stop doing something halfway

185
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,040
and then

186
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,400
do something else.

187
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:32,440
You could have asked the security guard

188
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,400
to let us come in

189
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:35,360
so that we could give them to you.

190
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:37,880
I don't want to let others know

191
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:38,880
where my home is.

192
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:41,360
Because it's not safe.

193
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,690
After all, you also know

194
00:08:42,909 --> 00:08:44,320
that I have a special job.

195
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:48,040
I can understand

196
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:49,800
your worries.

197
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,680
After all, to deal with you who deserve a beating,

198
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:54,400
it is likely that people will spray paint

199
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,920
on your house.

200
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:58,970
As a public figure, you can't lose temper.

201
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:04,520
Give the notes to me.

202
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:05,600
I'm going to catch the plane.

203
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,760
No notes for you!

204
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:09,160
You can't understand even if you have them.

205
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:14,600
Miss Tang, the last placeï¼Œ

206
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,280
come on.

207
00:09:15,800 --> 00:09:16,720
Don't get the last place

208
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:17,650
in the audition.

209
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:19,090
Come on! Come on!

210
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:24,640
Anyway, I don't want to

211
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:25,800
see the notes at all.

212
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:50,800
I recovered.

213
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:53,360
When you lost your temper just now,

214
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,600
you looked so cool.

215
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:58,690
What can I do?

216
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:01,120
How should I explain it to Mr. Huang?

217
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,840
Perhaps Mr. Huang just

218
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:04,080
said that casually.

219
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,720
I, I hope so.

220
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:09,020
You were really cool just now.

221
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:11,680
It made me feel very secure.

222
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,440
I'm flattered.

223
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:16,120
I just felt

224
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:18,120
that it would be OK if I stayed there alone.

225
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,440
But you were there with me.

226
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,760
So, I was mad at her.

227
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,920
I feel so happy.

228
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:26,680
Let's go. Let's go.

229
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:50,570
It is just around five o'clock, but it is already closed.

230
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,320
Dad,

231
00:10:58,280 --> 00:11:01,480
why did you close the restaurant at the supper time today?

232
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:03,680
Dad?

233
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:09,200
Li Haichao?

234
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:15,600
Ziqiu?

235
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,800
Ling Xiao, are you in?

236
00:11:27,800 --> 00:11:28,520
My dad...

237
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:31,010
You are in the hospital?

238
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:31,920
Who is sick?

239
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,980
The customer got food poisoning?

240
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:47,080
Dad,

241
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,180
what happened?

242
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,880
How come the customer got food poisoning?

243
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:50,920
Where is he now?

244
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:52,370
Where is he? Is he OK now?

245
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:54,120
Was he sure that he got food poisoning after having the noodles of our restaurant

246
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:54,640
or

247
00:11:54,640 --> 00:11:55,960
eating something else?

248
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:56,760
You asked so many questions

249
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:57,840
in one go.

250
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,240
Which question should I answer?

251
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,240
Answer me.

252
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:01,400
What should I say?

253
00:12:01,920 --> 00:12:02,850
Are you cooking?

254
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,280
I'm cooking noodles.

255
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:05,320
My noodles!

256
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,200
It spilled out.

257
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:14,160
Dad,

258
00:12:14,880 --> 00:12:15,680
did anyone take revenge on

259
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:16,840
our restaurant?

260
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:19,040
Our kitchen is so clean.

261
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,040
How come

262
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:21,240
cockroaches and flies

263
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,560
were found in food these days?

264
00:12:22,560 --> 00:12:23,200
Now,

265
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,880
a customer got food poisoning.

266
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:25,600
So,

267
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,060
what is the situation now?

268
00:12:27,520 --> 00:12:29,280
The customer who found a cockroach in the food last time

269
00:12:29,280 --> 00:12:30,880
called the food administration

270
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:32,210
and we have been warned.

271
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,120
This time,

272
00:12:33,400 --> 00:12:34,120
the customer who got food poisoning

273
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,200
also reported us to the administration.

274
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:35,960
Now we are compelled

275
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,960
to suspend business to bring up to standard.

276
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,160
To suspend business?

277
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:41,160
This is to force our family

278
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:42,120
to die.

279
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,000
Don't talk nonsense.

280
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:45,840
Come on.

281
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,240
It can't go so far.

282
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:48,800
No big deal.

283
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:51,320
It's just that we'll stop doing business for a week.

284
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:51,920
We can just

285
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,400
do a general cleaning

286
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:54,570
during this period.

287
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:56,600
The range hood

288
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:58,000
and ventilating fan

289
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,040
making noise in the kitchen

290
00:12:59,040 --> 00:13:00,640
should have long been replaced.

