926
00:35:13,480 --> 00:35:14,810
It's tomorrow evening.

927
00:35:15,880 --> 00:35:16,320
OK.

928
00:35:17,360 --> 00:35:19,090
I'll give you another 500 yuan,

929
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:20,680
