930
00:35:21,720 --> 00:35:23,180
Tell me if it's not enough.

931
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:23,880
No need.

932
00:35:23,960 --> 00:35:24,960
It's enough.

933
00:35:26,640 --> 00:35:27,440
Dad, you don't have to

934
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:28,360
work so hard.

935
00:35:28,880 --> 00:35:29,800
When I go to college,

936
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:30,520
I can

937
00:35:30,680 --> 00:35:32,740
do some part-time jobs to make money.

938
00:35:33,120 --> 00:35:34,650
What are you talking about?

939
00:35:35,080 --> 00:35:36,720
I want you to go to college,

940
00:35:36,720 --> 00:35:38,580
instead of doing part-time jobs.

941
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:40,400
Don't worry about money.

942
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:42,920
Our noodle restaurant

943
00:35:43,320 --> 00:35:44,320
is different now.

944
00:35:44,560 --> 00:35:46,240
It's no longer a small restaurant

945
00:35:46,240 --> 00:35:47,920
with just a few workers.

946
00:35:48,120 --> 00:35:49,450
It'll be a big noodle...

947
00:35:51,600 --> 00:35:52,640
I'll make

948
00:35:52,640 --> 00:35:53,920
a lot of money,

949
00:35:53,920 --> 00:35:55,250
so don't worry about it.

950
00:35:57,240 --> 00:35:58,240
Since you know

951
00:35:58,240 --> 00:35:59,840
how hard it is for Li Haichao,

952
00:36:00,280 --> 00:36:02,080
you should do something for him.

953
00:36:02,720 --> 00:36:04,450
You've never made money before

954
00:36:04,680 --> 00:36:05,800
and you don't know

955
00:36:05,800 --> 00:36:07,330
how hard it is to make money.

956
00:36:07,880 --> 00:36:09,480
You're about to go to college

957
00:36:09,960 --> 00:36:10,800
and Li Jianjian

958
00:36:10,800 --> 00:36:12,460
is about to go to college, too.

959
00:36:12,760 --> 00:36:13,480
It'll cost

960
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:14,920
a lot of money,

961
00:36:14,920 --> 00:36:15,680
you know?

962
00:36:16,120 --> 00:36:17,040
It's hard for an average family

963
00:36:17,040 --> 00:36:19,080
to support a college student,

964
00:36:19,080 --> 00:36:20,480
and he has to support two!

965
00:36:21,120 --> 00:36:22,580
Do you want to exhaust him?

966
00:36:26,520 --> 00:36:27,360
It's so late now.

967
00:36:27,360 --> 00:36:28,560
OK. I have to go now.

968
00:36:28,720 --> 00:36:29,360
I need to

969
00:36:29,360 --> 00:36:30,760
ask them to do something.

970
00:36:31,080 --> 00:36:32,640
What do you want to eat?

971
00:36:32,640 --> 00:36:33,640
Go and buy some

972
00:36:33,640 --> 00:36:34,770
in the supermarket.

973
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:36,180
By the way, Dad,

974
00:36:36,200 --> 00:36:37,520
would you like me to cook for lunch?

975
00:36:37,520 --> 00:36:39,120
It's easy to make some curry.

976
00:36:40,960 --> 00:36:41,600
OK.

977
00:36:42,360 --> 00:36:43,220
Do it on your own

978
00:36:43,600 --> 00:36:44,730
and don't get burnt.

979
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:45,690
Don't worry.

980
00:36:56,600 --> 00:36:59,000
Has Zhao Huaguang come to see you recently?

981
00:37:00,560 --> 00:37:01,120
No.

982
00:37:05,600 --> 00:37:06,680
OK. I'm leaving now.

983
00:37:06,680 --> 00:37:07,200
OK.

984
00:37:28,440 --> 00:37:29,200
Focus.

985
00:37:39,760 --> 00:37:40,480
We'll have curry for lunch

986
00:37:40,480 --> 00:37:41,440
and I'm going to buy some food in the supermarket.

987
00:37:41,440 --> 00:37:42,900
What would you like to eat?

988
00:37:42,960 --> 00:37:44,200
Two bags of original potato chips

989
00:37:44,200 --> 00:37:44,920
and crispy ice cream

990
00:37:44,920 --> 00:37:45,920
with chocolate on it.

991
00:37:45,920 --> 00:37:46,580
You know it.

992
00:37:47,080 --> 00:37:47,810
Watermelon.

993
00:37:48,320 --> 00:37:48,840
Money!

994
00:37:50,040 --> 00:37:50,960
Put it on my bill.

995
00:37:50,960 --> 00:37:51,560
Don't forget

996
00:37:51,560 --> 00:37:52,360
that you've already owed me

997
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:53,360
60 yuan this month.

998
00:37:53,360 --> 00:37:54,800
I'll pay you back when it's 100 yuan.

999
00:37:54,800 --> 00:37:55,800
Watermelon is a kind of fruit

1000
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,320
and it belongs to family expenses.

1001
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:58,180
My service fee!

1002
00:37:59,960 --> 00:38:01,440
How stingy!

1003
00:38:03,040 --> 00:38:04,080
Here you are.

1004
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:07,360
Where is my 5 yuan change?

1005
00:38:08,080 --> 00:38:09,360
Li Jianjian, lend me some money.

1006
00:38:09,360 --> 00:38:10,280
Again?

1007
00:38:10,280 --> 00:38:11,680
I've lent you 20 yuan.

1008
00:38:12,560 --> 00:38:14,220
I'll pay you back when it's 50.

1009
00:38:14,600 --> 00:38:15,400
Thank you.

1010
00:38:21,920 --> 00:38:22,360
Xiao,

1011
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:23,880
don't you want to go out and play

1012
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:25,560
after the college entrance exams?

1013
00:38:25,560 --> 00:38:26,320
No.

1014
00:38:26,320 --> 00:38:27,120
But I want.

1015
00:38:28,240 --> 00:38:29,760
You can go after finishing the homework.

1016
00:38:29,760 --> 00:38:31,520
Don't you have an exam before the holiday?

1017
00:38:31,520 --> 00:38:32,080
I'm afraid you can't get into

1018
00:38:32,080 --> 00:38:33,080
a beauty salon with your grades,

1019
00:38:33,080 --> 00:38:34,800
let alone Central Academy of Fine Arts.

1020
00:38:34,800 --> 00:38:36,080
I still have two more years

1021
00:38:36,080 --> 00:38:37,440
and I'm an art student.

1022
00:38:37,440 --> 00:38:38,700
I need just 300 points.

1023
00:38:48,160 --> 00:38:49,560
You made a mistake again.

1024
00:38:49,680 --> 00:38:50,880
I've told you not to hit me in the head.

1025
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:52,680
Will you marry me if I get hit out of my wits?

1026
00:38:52,680 --> 00:38:53,440
Yes, I will.

1027
00:38:56,680 --> 00:38:57,340
Yes, I will.

1028
00:39:42,280 --> 00:39:42,960
Ling Xiao!

1029
00:39:43,480 --> 00:39:44,240
Ling Xiao!

1030
00:39:44,720 --> 00:39:45,320
Yes?

1031
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:45,960
Hurry up!

1032
00:39:46,480 --> 00:39:47,440
your grandma has had a heart attack

1033
00:39:47,440 --> 00:39:48,440
and they're trying to save her.

1034
00:39:48,440 --> 00:39:49,440
I'm going to grab something upstairs.

1035
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:50,640
Let's go to the hospital right away.

1036
00:39:50,640 --> 00:39:51,200
Hurry up!

1037
00:39:53,520 --> 00:39:54,650
Xiao, just hurry up.

1038
00:40:01,960 --> 00:40:02,960
Hello, Chen Ting?

1039
00:40:03,760 --> 00:40:05,090
Are you on your way back?

1040
00:40:06,280 --> 00:40:07,760
I know you have no other choice.

1041
00:40:07,760 --> 00:40:10,600
[Emergency room]

1042
00:40:08,560 --> 00:40:10,480
Mom is in a particularly bad situation now

1043
00:40:10,480 --> 00:40:11,240
and the doctor has

1044
00:40:11,240 --> 00:40:13,240
given us the critical illness notice.

1045
00:40:13,240 --> 00:40:14,440
My wife and I are here.

1046
00:40:16,520 --> 00:40:17,040
OK.

1047
00:40:18,600 --> 00:40:19,760
When will she come back?

1048
00:40:19,760 --> 00:40:20,640
There's no tickets

1049
00:40:20,640 --> 00:40:22,840
and she'll come back tomorrow morning.

1050
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:25,040
Can she make it

1051
00:40:25,040 --> 00:40:26,160
to tomorrow?

1052
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:28,240
She has no other choice.

1053
00:40:28,360 --> 00:40:32,390
[Emergency room]

1054
00:40:29,280 --> 00:40:30,640
She shouldn't have married into another country.

1055
00:40:30,640 --> 00:40:32,370
