1056
00:40:32,760 --> 00:40:34,000
Mom is dying now,

1057
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:35,530
and she can't get back soon.

1058
00:40:35,880 --> 00:40:37,160
What's the point of saying this now?

1059
00:40:37,160 --> 00:40:38,360
It doesn't help at all.

1060
00:40:38,360 --> 00:40:39,440
Uncle, Aunt,

1061
00:40:39,880 --> 00:40:40,920
how is grandma?

1062
00:40:41,240 --> 00:40:42,720
They're still trying to save her.

1063
00:40:42,720 --> 00:40:43,680
A few days ago,

1064
00:40:43,680 --> 00:40:45,480
