1065
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:46,940
I asked her to see a doctor,

1066
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:48,280
but she refused

1067
00:40:48,480 --> 00:40:50,080
because she didn't want to waste money.

1068
00:40:50,080 --> 00:40:50,800
None of us had ever

1069
00:40:50,800 --> 00:40:52,200
