1070
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:53,450
so we didn't know it.

1071
00:40:53,760 --> 00:40:54,680
She could eat, drink

1072
00:40:54,680 --> 00:40:55,810
and shout at others,

1073
00:40:55,920 --> 00:40:57,380
