1076
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:01,720
but after that,

1077
00:41:01,720 --> 00:41:03,200
she was dying all of a sudden.

1078
00:41:03,200 --> 00:41:04,560
Calm down.

1079
00:41:04,840 --> 00:41:05,560
No one could

1080
00:41:05,560 --> 00:41:06,600
have expected it.

1081
00:41:06,710 --> 00:41:11,760
[Emergency room]

1082
00:41:07,200 --> 00:41:08,000
Is Chen Ting

1083
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:09,120
on her way here?

1084
00:41:09,240 --> 00:41:12,900
She didn't get the tickets and she'll come back tomorrow morning.

1085
00:41:14,640 --> 00:41:15,360
Well...

1086
00:41:19,320 --> 00:41:20,120
Oh.

1087
00:41:20,920 --> 00:41:22,680
OK, I got it.

1088
00:41:23,560 --> 00:41:24,560
I'm hanging up.

1089
00:41:28,720 --> 00:41:29,480
How is it?

1090
00:41:31,000 --> 00:41:32,600
Xiao won't come back today.

1091
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:34,480
They've got

1092
00:41:34,480 --> 00:41:36,680
the critical illness notice for four times

1093
00:41:36,680 --> 00:41:37,640
and the doctor said

1094
00:41:37,640 --> 00:41:39,880
that the family members should stay there.

1095
00:41:39,880 --> 00:41:41,520
