1098
00:41:45,040 --> 00:41:46,600
How did it become so serious?

1099
00:41:46,600 --> 00:41:47,600
She was energetic when she came here

1100
00:41:47,600 --> 00:41:49,330
to shout at Ling Xiao last time.

1101
00:41:51,600 --> 00:41:53,060
She's only in her sixties.

1102
00:41:54,600 --> 00:41:55,640
Don't think too much about it.

1103
00:41:55,640 --> 00:41:56,440
Let's eat now.

1104
00:41:57,320 --> 00:41:58,880
The curry that Ziqiu cooked

1105
00:41:58,880 --> 00:41:59,920
hasn't been touched yet.

1106
00:41:59,920 --> 00:42:00,520
I'm going to warm it up.

1107
00:42:00,520 --> 00:42:01,720
OK, Dad, let me take care of it.

1108
00:42:01,720 --> 00:42:02,720
I'll do it.

1109
00:42:04,120 --> 00:42:05,980
You make some shredded cucumber.

1110
00:42:06,280 --> 00:42:07,080
OK.
